Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.41,0:10:53.02,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.55,0:10:56.00,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}阿姨你是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.85,0:11:02.05,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}忘记了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.22,0:11:04.20,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不是说好了和妈妈一起努力的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.85,0:11:05.47,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}妈妈？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.60,0:11:07.08,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}对啊  是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.69,0:11:09.74,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}妈妈去了很远的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.80,0:11:11.77,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不用想那些
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.20,0:11:14.31,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我就是你的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.85,0:11:29.78,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.52,0:11:31.98,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}从今天开始重新来过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.01,0:11:35.45,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}在让你叫我妈妈那天到来以前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.87,0:11:37.20,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就叫我晴子阿姨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.32,0:11:44.84,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}观铃  我借来了这个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.95,0:11:47.04,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}看啊  有了这个就能出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.45,0:11:51.02,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}腿很疼走不动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.27,0:11:53.03,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所以才借了这个轮椅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.42,0:11:55.52,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}来  我来推着你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.98,0:11:58.74,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}一个人玩扑克牌更有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.34,0:12:01.13,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}来  两个人一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.37,0:12:03.92,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}到外边晒晒太阳多舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.10,0:12:06.17,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}还有很多很多有趣的事可以做哟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.87,0:12:14.34,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}风在吹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.94,0:12:16.12,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}在吹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.72,0:12:18.74,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}艳阳高照
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.22,0:12:20.21,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.75,0:12:23.01,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}知了嗡嗡地叫着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.30,0:12:24.60,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}吵得很呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.61,0:12:26.93,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.40,0:12:29.12,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是么  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.18,0:12:35.46,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.19,0:12:36.94,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}敬介…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.86,0:12:38.40,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.98,0:12:42.49,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}观铃  我是你的爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.28,0:12:44.75,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.76,0:12:50.10,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你也知道这孩子无法生活在人多的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.47,0:12:53.51,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所以才把她送来这个宁静的小镇中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.25,0:12:55.53,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不过看来是我错了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.82,0:12:56.82,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你还不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.96,0:12:58.65,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}她已经是我家的孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.85,0:13:00.81,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我已经得到了你父母的允许
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.19,0:13:02.48,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}她是我的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.78,0:13:03.87,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是我和你姐姐的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.22,0:13:05.72,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}觉得麻烦的时候送到我这
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.96,0:13:07.69,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}想起来时又要带她走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.93,0:13:09.96,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神尾家就是这样方便的地方吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.31,0:13:13.39,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我不能眼睁睁地看着在你身边生病的她不管
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.46,0:13:15.13,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不要在我面前讲普通话了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.17,0:13:17.13,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}听得我好恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.12,0:13:19.81,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}阿姨好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.24,0:13:22.20,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}抱歉  嚷嚷了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.45,0:13:24.68,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}阿姨… 吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.97,0:13:26.50,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不  不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.85,0:13:29.42,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}她一直叫我妈妈的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.13,0:13:31.84,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}观铃  我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.45,0:13:34.59,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}来  向晴子阿姨道谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.38,0:13:36.63,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}快  说谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.33,0:13:39.76,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}谢…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.79,0:13:40.69,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.78,0:13:42.49,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不要  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.84,0:13:44.31,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不要带走观铃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.85,0:13:46.46,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}她一直是孤零零一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.73,0:13:47.46,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是谁的责任呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.77,0:13:49.27,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不正是我们的责任吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.39,0:13:52.21,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所以我才决定要一直陪在她身边
