Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.45,0:13:57.11,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}晴子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.65,0:13:58.78,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我脑子不好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.94,0:14:01.01,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不知道这话该怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.29,0:14:02.70,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不过有一点可以肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.85,0:14:06.27,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}比起你我更想和她在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.57,0:14:07.96,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.45,0:14:11.67,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那就问问她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.99,0:14:12.61,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}观铃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.08,0:14:15.65,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}今后也想和晴子阿姨生活在一起吗
