Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.00,0:14:22.64,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}敬介
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.07,0:14:23.84,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}敬介你等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.07,0:14:24.61,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}三天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.05,0:14:26.01,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}给我三天时间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.35,0:14:29.04,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}如果三天后这孩子说不想和我在一起的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.16,0:14:31.15,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那我也就没什么可说的了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.47,0:14:33.84,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你带走她我也毫无怨言了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.37,0:14:36.52,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}求你了  敬介
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.87,0:14:41.69,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}三天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.34,0:14:45.73,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}三天能让我们找回母女亲情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.73,0:14:53.96,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}小观铃真的是非常喜欢恐龙啊
