Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.84,0:15:01.02,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嘿  还真像我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.24,0:15:03.13,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这个是「速龙（恐爪龙）」（Velociraptor）
