Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.23,0:15:20.07,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好热
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.69,0:15:21.52,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.89,0:15:23.65,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不过忍耐一会就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.22,0:15:26.27,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}到了海边应该会更凉爽
