Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.57,0:15:34.31,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不要说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.37,0:15:36.10,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那样的话便当不就白做了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.14,0:15:37.01,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}回去…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.24,0:15:39.10,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}里面有甜甜的炸鸡蛋哟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.20,0:15:41.27,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是观铃点的菜哟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.55,0:15:42.87,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我们好好地玩一天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.13,0:15:43.62,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.28,0:15:46.68,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真的要回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.02,0:15:47.63,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}回去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.31,0:15:50.99,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那我做的便当怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.03,0:15:51.74,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不管
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.05,0:15:57.62,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}…那我不管你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.88,0:16:00.54,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那么想一个人玩的话就自己回去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.78,0:16:01.31,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}傻瓜！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.24,0:16:13.10,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好热啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.77,0:16:15.09,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}头晕眼花
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.98,0:16:20.69,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哇！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.80,0:16:28.78,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嘎哦…
